---
// Intro to the digital garden section on the homepage.
---

<section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-20">
  <hr class="border-gray-800 mb-20" />

  <div class="mb-10">
    <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-gray-500 font-mono mb-3">01 / The garden</p>
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold accent-underline">Thinking in public</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] gap-10 items-start">
    <div class="space-y-5 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-lg max-w-2xl">
      <p>
        This is where I collect essays, notes, reflections, book reviews, poems, and unfinished thoughts. Some pieces are polished, others are still growing.
      </p>
      <p>
        The goal isn't to look like I have everything figured out — it's to think out loud about software, mindfulness, ethics, AI, creativity, and building a meaningful life.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="font-mono text-xs text-gray-500 space-y-2 md:text-right">
      <div>
        <span class="text-gray-400">Essays</span>
        <span class="text-gray-600"> · long-form</span>
      </div>
      <div>
        <span class="text-gray-400">Notes</span>
        <span class="text-gray-600"> · short thoughts</span>
      </div>
      <div>
        <span class="text-gray-400">Projects</span>
        <span class="text-gray-600"> · what I build</span>
      </div>
      <div>
        <span class="text-gray-400">Reviews</span>
        <span class="text-gray-600"> · books, talks</span>
      </div>
      <div>
        <span class="text-gray-400">Poems</span>
        <span class="text-gray-600"> · the soft stuff</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
